{"tid":1167411,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"西區單位傳臭味 消防破門揭發男子燒炭亡","createTime":"2019-05-23T04:36:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-23T05:42:18.000Z","uid":41404,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"1d837a90986db5ebb099fa8a541faa4877fda592","tid":1167411,"uid":41404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-23T04:36:02.000Z","msg":"西區第三街129-133號豐盛大廈，早上9時24分，保安員接獲住客投訴，指其中一單位傳出臭味，保安員報警求助，消防到場破門而入，發現一名年約50多歲男子在單位內燒炭自殺，救護員經檢驗後證實事主當場死亡。警方正調查事件。<br />\n<br />\n24小時求助熱線︰<br />\n香港撒瑪利亞防止自殺會熱線︰23892222<br />\n撒瑪利亞會熱線(多種語言)︰28960000<br />\n生命熱線︰23820000<br />\n東華三院芷若園熱線︰18281<br />\n社會福利署熱線︰23432255<br />\n醫院管理局精神健康專線(24小時精神健康熱線諮詢服務)：24667350<br />\n明愛向晴熱線：18288<br />\n賽馬會青少年情緒健康網上支援平台「Open噏」：<a href=\"http://www.openup.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.openup.hk&d=z4MUysNBbosN1Ywc1Uoyo5IBJzpNVIoVNH6FP0f0bDA%3D&h=168b8418\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">www.openup.hk</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20190523/59631824\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190523%2F59631824&d=z4MUysNBbosN1Ywc1Uoyo5IBJzpNVIoVNH6FP0f0bDA%3D&h=e2150c01\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190523%2F59631824&h=a832294a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20190523/59631824</a>"},{"pid":"eab07d2e5d0b1264d0d2f7fecf16c4326b4a9192","tid":1167411,"uid":9031,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-23T05:14:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1522f2472fb5f9001a85b23274bf1677ab310922","tid":1167411,"uid":164240,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-23T05:18:42.000Z","msg":"睇錯個西傳出臭味"},{"pid":"8e3644609c642bf87f245b0b337ff1ca91d08dc3","tid":1167411,"uid":4273,"like":1,"dislike":0,"scor